Big Brother Titans housemate, Jaypee has revealed that she is addicted to sex. Jaypee made this known during a conversation with Ebubu on Friday. The nurse said her friends calls her a “Nymphomaniac. “I am a sex addict, my friends call me a Nymphomaniac. “I love sex. Since yesterday I have been losing my mind. I am so horny like I am going crazy. “I’m that girl that guys meet and realized they don’t love sex like I do. If I am with you, you are going enjoy the benefit.”